<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-2951] Cannot override instance methodMissing() in ExpandoMetaClass</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2951</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is not possible to provide an instance-level &lt;tt&gt;methodMissing()&lt;/tt&gt; implementation for a class via ExpandoMetaClass. Note that it &lt;em&gt;is&lt;/em&gt; possible to do this for the static version of the method. See the attached test case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12814224">GROOVY-2951</key>
            <summary>Cannot override instance methodMissing() in ExpandoMetaClass</summary>
